10 breach affecting a consumer, notify the consumer that there has been a data
11 broker security breach. Notice of the security breach shall be made in the most
12 expedient time possible and without unreasonable delay, but not later than 45
13 days after the discovery or notification, consistent with the legitimate needs of
14 the law enforcement agency, as provided in subdivisions (3) and (4) of this
15 subsection, or with any measures necessary to determine the scope of the
16 security breach and restore the reasonable integrity, security, and
17 confidentiality of the data system.
